	* subr.el (syntax-after): Doc fix.
	(syntax-class): If argument is nil, return nil.  Mask off upper 16
	bits, not 8 bits.

	* files.el (mode-require-final-newline): Doc fix.
	(backup-buffer-copy): Fix last change.

