	* generic.el: Fix commentary section.  Don't require cl for
	compilation.
	(generic-mode-list): Add autoload cookie.
	(generic-use-find-file-hook, generic-lines-to-scan)
	(generic-find-file-regexp, generic-ignore-files-regexp)
