	(reb-lisp-mode): Require `rx' feature when `re-reb-syntax' is `rx'.
	(reb-lisp-syntax-p, reb-change-syntax): `rx' is a Lisp syntax.
	(reb-cook-regexp): Call `rx-to-string' when `re-reb-syntax' is `rx'.

