	* progmodes/compile.el (compile-internal): Use point, not point-min,
	for set-window-point.

	* textmodes/tex-mode.el (latex-find-indent): Avoid error at end of buf.

	* emacs-lisp/lisp-mnt.el (lm-section-end): Require outline.

